Purple ZNC Helper
=================

To install the plugin, simply extract the contents of the folder "pidgin" in this zip file to your
pidgin install directory, which is "C:\Program Files\Pidgin" by default, or to your .purple user dir.

After activating the plugin you have to tick the option "Uses ZNC Bouncer" in the preferences of your IRC account in order to have it work with the specific account. Please make sure that you have set the timestamp format of ZNC to "[%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S]" and that it will be appended to the message.

Have fun. :o)

